00:52:59,836 --> 00:53:01,589
Itu tak sulit.

452
00:53:02,401 --> 00:53:04,020
Baiklah.

453
00:53:19,505 --> 00:53:21,133
Ibu?

454
00:53:24,768 --> 00:53:27,230
Ada apa, Kawan?
Dia ada di dalam. Ayo.

455
00:53:28,985 --> 00:53:31,741
Ibu tak ingin kau khawatir.

456
00:53:31,909 --> 00:53:34,330
Ibumu tak akan pergi
ke mana-mana, mengerti?

457
00:53:34,498 --> 00:53:36,961
Ya?

458
00:53:37,129 --> 00:53:39,091
- Selesaikan tugasmu.
- Baiklah.

459
00:54:22,650 --> 00:54:24,278
Halo?

460
00:54:25,616 --> 00:54:28,120
Petugas polisi ada
di luar sini.

461
00:54:29,958 --> 00:54:32,087
Boleh aku meminta bensin?

